## Tips before your electrician visit in Bandipora

- **Note which rooms or circuits are affected** and when the problem started.
- **Keep children and pets away** from open boards until the visit.
- **Clear access** to the switchboard and affected sockets.
- **Mention inverter or generator setup** if you have backup power.
- **Be home or arrange access** so the electrician can show you the fault and approve the work.

